<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>On the "Create a Layout" page of the QuickStart, the code sample for the bootstrap.php file contains the following line that references the path to the scripts directory:</p>

<p>Zend_Layout::startMvc(APPLICATION_PATH . '/layouts/scripts');</p>

<p>Based on the directory structure outlined on the "Set Up the Project Structure" page, I believe this should be:</p>

<p>Zend_Layout::startMvc(APPLICATION_PATH . '/views/scripts');</p>

    </div>
